text:
Boy, was I in for a big surprise
when I moved here.

I thought this
was going to be a dead town

with nothing happening.
This one?

Then I found out
there were you little guys,
real outer space aliens.

Dude? You're going to
vaporize me?

Come on. Let me tuck you in
nice and tight.

- ( sneezes )
- Whoa!

My mom and sister are,
like, perfect.
Me? Not so much--

with the exception of
baby-sitting you aliens,
which I pretty much rule at.

Your hair's going to
look so dope.

You're totally not going to
be able to see
your antennae sticking out.

Maybe we should rethink
this one a little.

And to think, you need me
to baby-sit you all.

Once upon a time
in a land far, far away--

- ( chomp )
- Hey!

I was so wrong
about this place.

I think I'm going to
like it here.
Okay, this one has to work.
Great!

So, uh, how do you
put this on, exactly?

All-new series, "Gabby Duran
& The Unsittables,"

premieres Friday, October 11th
on Disney Channel.

When you said
you liked this book,

I thought you meant
to read not to eat.
( burps )
